{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9639877b8b","title":"对吴法宪检讨信的几条批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"68ab45b29e","index":0,"year":1970,"month":10,"day":14,"articleId":"9639877b8b","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"林彪","id":"cce608ea44","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"李德生","id":"f3ee2f4a99","type":"人物"},{"name":"吴法宪","id":"fa1994871e","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8decf6b751","type":"title","text":"对吴法宪检讨信的几条批注","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"113a26b381","type":"paragraph","text":"对吴宪法检讨信的几条批注","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c306344b0f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ac6c4eeaa","type":"paragraph","text":"1970.10.14","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1698fcece","type":"paragraph","text":"作为一个共产党人，为什么这样缺乏正大光明的气概。由几个人发难，企图欺骗200多个中央委员，有党以来，没有见过。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dbc3e2e160","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组各同志（除个别同志如李德生外）忘记了九大通过的党章、林彪同志的报告，又找什么天才问题，不过是一个借口。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8caf4dbe0c","type":"paragraph","text":"什么伟大谦虚，在原则性问题上，从来没有客气过。要敢于反潮流。反潮流是马列主义的一个原则。在庐山，我的态度就是一次反潮流。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1af0bc4703","type":"paragraph","text":"这句话并没有错，中央委员会有严重的斗争。有斗争是正常生活。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9639877b8b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}